# Windsurf Rules - Customer App

## Project: Patient Medical App (Australia)

### Core Principles (MUST FOLLOW)

**KISS** - Keep It Simple
- Simple > clever
- One function = one job
- No over-engineering

**SOLID**
- Single Responsibility
- Open/Closed
- Liskov Substitution
- Interface Segregation
- Dependency Inversion

**DRY** - Don't Repeat Yourself
- Extract reusable code
- Constants for magic values
- No copy-paste

### Tech Stack
- React Native + Expo
- TypeScript (strict)
- React Query
- Zustand
- Zod validation

### Naming
- Components: PascalCase
- Functions: camelCase
- Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
- Types: IPascalCase / TPascalCase

### Limits
- File: 150 lines max
- Function: 50 lines max
- Props: 5 max
- Nesting: 3 levels max

### ALWAYS
- Full TypeScript (no any)
- Handle errors
- Handle loading
- Validate inputs
- Use constants
- Test critical paths

### NEVER
- any type
- @ts-ignore
- console.log in prod
- Plain text secrets
- Commit API keys
- Skip error handling

### Security (Medical)
- Mask Medicare numbers
- HTTPS only
- Validate inputs
- Australian Privacy Act compliance

### Reference
Full rules: /rules/PROJECT_RULES.md
